Hello all.

This script is a modification of the command that I run to find changes on the 
DDC controls. I thought it could be useful to some user else. 

Run "./ddcdiff -h" and if the device is correct, run "./ddcdiff". Manipulate 
the monitor buttons, press Enter and see the changed controls in console and 
in a log file.

Regards
lardhan



